| Code | Clade |
|------|-------|
| fv | Formal Verification & Proofs |
| nl | Nextgen Languages |
| rm | Repo Management & Tooling |
| gv | Governance & Standards |
| db | Databases |
| ap | Applications |
| ix | Infrastructure & Cloud |
| dx | Developer Ecosystem |
| pt | Protocols & Interop |
| ax | AI & Neurosymbolic |
| gm | Games & Interactive |
| sc | Security |

## SESSION STARTUP CHECKLIST

- Read THIS file first
- Understand: this is the central registry, not a code project
- Never modify repo seed data without understanding the pointer authority model
